      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Crack the <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into a shallow bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and beat lightly with a fork</p><p>Add a small handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a plate and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to another plate with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and give everything a good mix up until all the breadcrumbs are coated in the oil</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1655800447144-x200.jpg",
