    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Top, tail and peel 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>into a pile of ribbons, then grate the <strong>remaining carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
