    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 300ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [600ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and reduce the heat to low</p><p>Add the <strong>soy sauce</strong> and stir through the <strong>mango chutney</strong></p><p>Cook for 5-7 min or until the sauce has thickened to a curry-like consistency</p><p>Once cooked, season with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> – this is your <strong>katsu sauce</strong></p>",
