    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>rice vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>in a large bowl  – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred roughly</p><p>Add the<strong> shredded lettuce</strong> to the dressing with the <strong>carrot ribbons</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p>",
