      "instruction": "<p>To serve, spoon the<strong> katsu sauce</strong> onto the plate, then lay the<strong> crispy aubergine rounds</strong> over the sauce</p><p>Serve the<strong> cooked rice </strong>and <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
